Fun fact about this tattoo: I googled “swords” because I wasn’t entirely sure how to draw the hilt of the sword, and wanted to look at some references. Found some really cool images to work off of. Little did I know, the sword I wound up drawing is almost identical to a sword from Lord of the Rings. I’ve never seen LOTR, so I had no idea. 😂 But, it worked out, because the client was a big fan of LOTR, and figured it was intentional. Happy accidents 😂❤️
